A year ago I made a commitment to myself to abstain from alcohol or any other substances for the entire year… and tonight I cross the finish line 🏁 

Shout out to all everyone that helped me accomplish this goal for me this year! 

4 weddings / Bachelor Parties / 1 Month Jack Daniel’s shoot / Lake Days - was no match! 💪🏻

Going to be doing another 30 day very disciplined January - feel free to join me 

January Focus Mode Habits:
- 4:45am - wake up everyday
- 10 min meditation 
- Gym
- Cold Shower / Ice Bath
- 1 hr before bed no screens 
- 30 Min - Reading
- No Alcohol / Substances 
- No processed Sugars 

#discipline #nye
Just some of my favorite things 🏂🎥🤘🏻
